                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "D'où vient que ma pensée encor revole à toi,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Grec illustre à qui nul ne songe, excepté moi ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "D'où vient que me voilà, seul et dans la nuit noire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Grave et triste, essayant de redorer ta gloire ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Tandis que là, dehors, cent rhéteurs furieux",
